OWESIFAZANE ushonile kwathi ababili balimala kabi namhlanje ekuseni ngesikhathi iveni ishayisa neloli emgwaqweni u603, e-Eston, KwaZulu-Natal. Okhulumela inkampani i-ER24, uMnuz Russel Meiring, uthe abezimo eziphuthumayo bafike endaweni yesigameko ngezithuba zabo-9.20 ekuseni, bathole ukuthi iveni neloli kushayisene. “Lezi ziguli ezintathu zitholwe eveni.” Uthe ocaningweni elenziwe ngabezempilo luveze ukuthi owesifazane, okukholelwa ukuthi uneminyaka ebalelwa ku-70, ulimale kabi futhi usesimweni esibucayi. “Iziguli ezimbili zitholakale zilimale okujwayeleke. Abezimo eziphuthumayo balaphe iziguli futhi banikeza isalukazi usizo oluphuthumayo. Ngesikhashana lowesifazane ugcine eshonile yize enikezwe konke ukunakekelwa okufanele,” kusho uMeiring. Eqhuba uthe lezi ziguli ezimbili ziphuthunyiswe ezibhedlela eziseduze ukuze bathole unyango oluthe thuthu. “Amaphoyisa afikile endaweni yesigameko ukuzokwenza uphenyo,” kusho uMeiring.